ASSETS

All in-game art is generated procedurally from scratch by
`assets/generate_assets.py`. None of it is derived from Factorio or any other
copyrighted source. These generated images are dedicated to the public domain
under the Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal dedication
(https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/). You may use them for any
purpose without attribution.

AutoFactorio is an independent, fan-made, simplified logistics game inspired by
the genre. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by Wube Software (Factorio).
